PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, of the Acts of the XXIV CONGRESS of the UNIVERSAL POSTAL UNION being held in Geneva, between July 23 and August 12, 2008; (b) to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other members of the Canadian delegation to sign those Acts on behalf of the Government of Canada.
